# PageCache Phase 4 upstream xfstests acceptance list
# Goal: validate ext4 PageCache integration only with upstream xfstests cases.
# No self-developed PageCache smoke/coherency tests are required for Phase 4
# acceptance unless these upstream cases expose a blocker that needs reduction.
#
# Coverage:
# - generic/091: fsx O_DIRECT with sub-block sizes and concurrent buffered I/O
# - generic/130: buffered/direct coherency, holes, direct EOF zeroing
# - generic/133: concurrent buffered/direct readers and writers on one file
# - generic/208: AIO DIO read-cache invalidation race
# - generic/209: sync DIO invalidation of readahead/page cache
# - generic/247: direct I/O and mmap writer race
# - generic/263: fsx direct I/O vs sub-block buffered I/O
# - generic/366: mixed direct read/write and buffered write hang regression
# - generic/412: direct I/O + buffered write + truncate into hole durability
# - generic/418: explicit pagecache invalidation for buffered/direct mixtures
# - generic/469: truncate-down must zero page cache beyond new EOF
# - generic/749: mmap EOF partial-page zero-fill and SIGBUS boundary semantics
# - generic/751: page-cache truncation + writeback stress

generic/091
generic/130
generic/133
generic/208
generic/209
generic/247
generic/263
generic/366
generic/412
generic/418
generic/469
generic/749
generic/751
